    BOp, IGroupMemberNode, IQueryNode, IVariableBindingRequirements, IPropertySet, Serializable, Cloneable

    public class LoadGraph
extends GraphUpdate
    The LOAD operation reads an RDF document from a IRI and inserts its triples into the specified graph in the Graph Store. 
     LOAD ( SILENT )? IRIref_from ( INTO GRAPH IRIref_to )?
    Author:
    Bryan Thompson
    See Also:
    http://www.w3.org/TR/sparql11-update/#load, Serialized Form
